title: Arsenal are officially by the ‘most injured’ team in the Premier League – losing players for TWO YEARS longer than Manchester United in the last five seasons
text:
EFL Gunned down Arsenal are officially by the ‘most injured’ team in the Premier League – losing players for TWO YEARS longer than Manchester United in the last five seasons 
Arsene Wenger's men have missed a total of 10,825 days through injury, totalling 28 years on the physio's table By Dave Fraser
